CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 3, 1962, pg. 14A, reads: " Yvonne Kemp...this young lovely was a dream in a bathing suit called 'The Checkerboard.'"
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Yvonne Jones Kemp wearing two toned block patterned bathing suit, carrying dark towel with light colored stripes, standing barefoot in front of musicians in Holiday House for the D. I. Club's "Melody of Fashion" benefit for MENDS
